                  main PROC
;;;12005  //===============================================
;;;12006  int main (void)

;;;12023  
;;;12024  //init_timer( 0,SystemFrequency/2000/4 - 1 ); // 1ms	
;;;12025  //enable_timer( 0 );
;;;12026  
;;;12027  SET_REG(LPC_GPIO0->FIODIR, 0, 27, 1);
